<doc id="811954" wikidata="Q6916735" url="?curid=811954" title="Most Beloved">
<text>Most Beloved or Beloved () is an album by Leslie Cheung released in 1995 after a long personal struggle between deciding to make a comeback or to make good his retirement vow. It was also his first album with Rock Records.

It marked the milestone of another chapter of Leslie Cheung&#x27;s career as it was his first album after supposedly retiring from the music world six years ago at the height of his career.

