A 680-page volume, &quot;Dylan Dog Casefiles&quot;, was released in 2009 (), to tie in with the movie &quot;Dylan Dog: Dead of Night&quot;. It reprinted the seven stories Dark Horse previously released. This volume also includes cover art by Mike Mignola.

